cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.SI, cs.LG 

The paper deals with voice conversion techniques and their performance under mismatched conditions, which involves signal processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SD (Sound), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the paper involves natural language processing. The paper also involves objective evaluation of different techniques, which falls under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the paper involves statistical analysis and comparison of different techniques, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
